  "title": "Methods for rearing Heliocheilus albipunctella in the laboratory and eliminating the pupal diapause",
  "abstract": "The life cycle of head miner (H. albipunctella) infesting pearl millet are presented. Methods for rearing the head miner in the laboratory and eliminating the diapause stage of the pest to improve its management in the field are also discussed.",
